  {
    "hotel_id": "148914",
    "hotel_url": "https://www.agoda.com/radisson-blu-edwardian-vanderbilt-hotel/hotel/basildon-gb.html",
    "name": "Radisson Blu Hotel, London South Kensington (formerly Vanderbilt)",
    "detail": "This is one of the best London hotels I have stayed in - and I have been visiting London for many, many years now. The location is absolutely terrific - a minute's walk from Gloucester Road tube station, Waitrose just across the road, a buzz of cafes and restaurants all around. It made it easy to catch a tube to my early morning flight from Heathrow. The hotel itself is clean and the staff couldn't have been more friendly and helpful. The room was adequate, but basic and small and poky (like pretty much all London hotels). However, the bathroom was a lovely surprise - bright, spacious and modern. The room could do with some attention to bring it to par with the bathroom and the rest of the hotel. Breakfast was at their restaurant, Scott & Banter, and was really interesting with tons of healthy options and a wide range of fruit juices. This will definitely be my first choice on future trips to London.",
